Anna Ebiere Banner (amụrụ na 18 Febrụwarị 1995) bụ nwaafọ Nigeria nke mmeri na emume nwayị kacha nma bekwa ọnye na eme ịhe egwurịegwu
O kpuru okpueze na Most Beautiful Girl in Nigeria na afo 2013 nke ọnye kpubereya okpu bu ọnye meriri na afo 2012 MBGN bu Queen Isabella Ayuk
Ọ nọchitere anya Naịgeria na asumunpị Miss World  2013
A họpụtara ya onye enyemaka pụrụ iche na omenaala na njem nlegharị anya nke Gọvanọ Henry Dickson na ọchịchị ya dịka Nwa agbogho kacha ma mma na Naịgeria n'afọ 2012
Na 2014, o mere ịhe nkịrị izizi na Super Story
